\frac{(4k-15)\pi}8
n+2k\pi
k\in\mathbb Z
n\in(-\pi,\pi]
\boxed{\bf My\,try::}
\begin{align} \frac{(4k-15)\pi}{8}&=\frac{4k\pi-15\pi}{8}\\ &=\frac{4k\pi-16\pi+\pi}{8}\\ &=\frac{4(k\pi-4\pi)+\pi}{8}\\&=\frac{k\pi-4\pi}2+\pi/8 \end{align}
