k=2\ell
\ell\in\Bbb{Z}
\frac{4k-15}{8}\pi=\frac{8\ell-15}{8}\pi=(\ell-2)\pi+\frac{\pi}{8}
k
k=2\ell+1
\ell\in\Bbb{Z}
